dataIdInfo.idAbs:
This dataset is a product of United Nations OCHA produced in collaboration with the Common Operation Dataset (COD) sub working group in Mali. This product is developed to support all humanitarian operations within Mali and is not to be sold.

The boundaries and names shown and the designations used in the dataset do not imply official endorsement or acceptance by the United Nations.

Coordinate System: GCS_WGS_1984

Scale: 1M

Credits to: UNOCHA and COD Sub Working Group in Mali.

Primary data source: Direction Nationale des Collectivités Territroriales (DNCT), Mali

Secondary data source: United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs (OCHA)

Produced on: 29 May 2019

Consts.useLimit: See the COD/FOD Registry Terms of Use. This does not replace any terms of use information provided with the dataset.

dataIdInfo.idCredit: UNOCHA and COD Sub Working Group in Mali

dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following was found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Admin0 Name changed to French short name "Mali (le)". 2. Created and populated reference name field. 3. Found and fixed 3 gap errors and 1 overlap error.
